    <claim num="1">
      <claim-text>What is claimed is:</claim-text>
      <claim-text>1.</claim-text>
      <claim-text>A pharmaceutical composition in solid form comprising bupropion hydrochloride and fumaric acid, wherein the ratio of fumaric acid to bupropion hydrochloride by weight is from about 0.05 to about 2 0 (slashed zero)</claim-text>
    </claim>
    <claim num="2">
      <claim-text>2. A composition as in claim 1, wherein the ratio of fumaric acid to bupropion hydrochloride by weight is from about 0.1 to about 1.2.</claim-text>
    </claim>
    <claim num="3">
      <claim-text>3. A composition as in claim 1, wherein the ratio of fumaric acid to bupropion hydrochloride by weight is from about 0.2 to about 0.8.</claim-text>
    </claim>
    <claim num="4">
      <claim-text>4. A composition as in claim 1 in the form of a tablet.</claim-text>
    </claim>
